# Currency Converter

A modern and responsive currency converter built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. The application fetches real-time exchange rates and dynamically updates country flags to provide a clean and intuitive user experience.

## Live Demo

<https://shreetanu205-sudo.github.io/CurrencyConverter/>

## ✨ Features

- Real-time currency conversion
- 30+ supported currencies
- Dynamic country flags
- Modern dark-themed UI
- Responsive design
- Input validation
- Automatic default currencies (USD → INR)

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (ES6)
- Fetch API

## APIs Used

### 1. Frankfurter API

Used to fetch real-time exchange rates.

**Base URL**

<https://api.frankfurter.dev/v1/latest>

Example:

<https://api.frankfurter.dev/v1/latest?amount=1&from=USD&to=INR>

Official Website:

<https://frankfurter.dev/>

### 2. Flags API

Used to display country flags corresponding to selected currencies.

**Base URL**

<https://flagsapi.com/>

Example:

<https://flagsapi.com/US/flat/64.png>

Official Website:

<https://flagsapi.com/>

